        <scopecontent id="ref8">
            <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
            <p>The Burning Water Archive is a collection of correspondence to the editors, Edward Kissam and Paul Boorstin, from 1962 to 1968. Collection highlights include letters written by Carol Bergé, Robert Bly, Ted Enslin, Clayton Eschleman, and Gary Snyder.</p>
        </scopecontent>
        <arrangement id="ref9">
            <head>Arrangement</head>
            <p>The correspondence in the collection is arranged alphabetically. The issues of the journal are organized chronologically.</p>
            <list numeration="arabic" type="ordered">
                <item>Series I: Correspondence and Issues of Burning Water</item>
            </list>
        </arrangement>
        <separatedmaterial id="ref23">
            <head>Separated Material</head>
            <p>There is no information about materials that are associated by provenance to the described materials that have been physically separated or removed.</p>
        </separatedmaterial>
